Package com.sk.objects

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Card
    Class creates a Card object, which is a representation of 1 card in a deck of cards
    CardTest
    Unit tests for Card class
    Dealer
    Class implements the Participant interface and creates a Dealer object
    DealerTest
    Unit tests for Dealer class
    Deck
    Class creates the Deck object, which represents a deck of cards in the game
    DeckTest
    Unit tests for Deck class
    Hand
    Class creates a Hand object representing the hand (i.e., all the cards that have been dealt to a participant)
    HandTest
    Unit tests for Hand class
    MoneyPot
    Class creates a MoneyPot objects, which represents the total amount of money that a Player object can play with during a session
    MoneyPotTest
    Unit Tests for MoneyPot class
    Player
    Class implements the Participant interface and creates a Player object
    PlayerTest
    Unit tests for Player class
